Cocoa Farm Visit Rubrics

changelog: all ^S_FID1$ variables are now ^S_FID$

Pest Management

cocoavars1 <- grep("^S_FID$|^B2_.|^E1_.|^E2_.|^E3_.", names(cocoavisit), value=TRUE) #select only pest management variables
pestgap <- cocoavisit[cocoavars1] #data table for pest GAP
cocoavars1full <- grep("^E1_.|^E2_.|^E3_.", names(pestgap), value=TRUE) #select only countable score variables
pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
pestgap[grep("^E2_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(pestgap[grep("^E2_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
pestgap[grep("^E3_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(pestgap[grep("^E3_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
pestgap$NAcheck <- ifelse((apply(pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(pestgap[grep("^E2_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))) & (apply(pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(pestgap[grep("^E3_.",cocoavars1,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))),"1",NA) #checks that for every observation component the same number of trees have been checked
pestgap$scoreE1 <- (rowSums(pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(pestgap[grep("^E1_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
pestgap$scoreE2 <- (rowSums(pestgap[grep("^E2_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(pestgap[grep("^E2_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
pestgap$scoreE3 <- (rowSums(pestgap[grep("^E3_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(pestgap[grep("^E3_.",cocoavars1full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
pestgap$evaluation <- ifelse(is.na(pestgap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) > 0.2,"No Evidence of Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) > 0.1 & apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) <= 0.2,"Evidence of Minimum Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) > 0.05 & apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) <= 0.1,"Evidence of Good Adoption",
                                    ifelse(apply(pestgap[c("scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3")], 1, max) <= 0.05,"Evidence of Excellent Adoption","NA"))))) #evaluation of all criteria together
pestgapfinal <- (pestgap[c("S_FID","NAcheck","scoreE1","scoreE2","scoreE3","evaluation")]) #filter only cases for cass only
colnames(pestgapfinal)[1] <- "C1"
write.table(pestgapfinal, "CocoaFarm_pestManagement.txt", sep="\t")
print(head(pestgapfinal))

Weed Management

cocoavars2 <- grep("^S_FID$|^G1_.|^G3_.", names(cocoavisit), value=TRUE) #select only weed management variables
weedgap <- cocoavisit[cocoavars2] #data table for weed GAP
cocoavars2full <- grep("^G1_.|^G3_.", names(weedgap), value=TRUE) #select only countable score variables
weedgap[grep("^G1_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(weedgap[grep("^G1_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0.5;3=0;else=NA") #recoding values
weedgap[grep("^G3_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(weedgap[grep("^G3_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
weedgap$NAcheck <- ifelse((apply(weedgap[grep("^G1_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(weedgap[grep("^G3_.",cocoavars2,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))),"1",NA) #checks that for every observation component the same number of trees have been checked
weedgap$scoreG1 <- (rowSums(weedgap[grep("^G1_.",cocoavars2full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(weedgap[grep("^G1_.",cocoavars2full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
weedgap$scoreG3 <- (rowSums(weedgap[grep("^G3_.",cocoavars2full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(weedgap[grep("^G3_.",cocoavars2full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
weedgap$evaluation <- ifelse(is.na(weedgap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) > 0.5,"No Evidence of Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) > 0.3 & apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) <= 0.5,"Evidence of Minimum Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) > 0.15 & apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) <= 0.3,"Evidence of Good Adoption",
                                    ifelse(apply(weedgap[c("scoreG1")], 1, max) <= 0.15,"Evidence of Excellent Adoption","NA"))))) #evaluation of all criteria together
weedgap$evaluationplus <- ifelse(is.na(weedgap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(weedgap[c("scoreG3")], 1, max) >= 0.5,"Additionaly Evidence of Ground-Cover","No Additional Evidence of Ground-Cover")) #evaluation extra criteria
weedgapfinal <- (weedgap[c("S_FID","NAcheck","scoreG1","scoreG3","evaluation","evaluationplus")]) #filter only cases for cass only
colnames(weedgapfinal)[1] <- "C1"
write.table(weedgapfinal, "CocoaFarm_weedManagement.txt", sep="\t")
print(head(weedgapfinal))

Cocoa Tree Pruning

cocoavars3 <- grep("^S_FID$|^B2_.|^C1_.|^C2_.|^C3_.|^D2_.|^D3_.|^D4_.|^D1_.", names(cocoavisit), value=TRUE) #select only prun management variables
prungap <- cocoavisit[cocoavars3] #data table for prun GAP
cocoavars3full <- grep("^B2_.|^C1_.|^C2_.|^C3_.|^D2_.|^D3_.|^D4_.|^D1_.", names(prungap), value=TRUE) #select only countable score variables
prungap[grep("^C1_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^C1_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=0.5;2=0;3=1;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^C2_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^C2_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=0.5;2=0;3=1;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^C3_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^C3_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;3=1;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^D1_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^D1_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^D2_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^D2_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^D3_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^D3_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap[grep("^D4_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(prungap[grep("^D4_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
prungap$NAcheck <- ifelse((apply(prungap[grep("^C1_.|^C2_.|^C3_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(prungap[grep("^D2_.|^D3_.|^D4_.",cocoavars3,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))),"1",NA) #checks that for every observation component the same number of trees have been checked
prungap$scoreC <- (rowSums(prungap[grep("^C1_.|^C2_.|^C3_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * apply(prungap[grep("^C1_.|^C2_.|^C3_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x)))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
prungap$scoreD <- (rowSums(prungap[grep("^D2_.|^D3_.|^D4_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * apply(prungap[grep("^D2_.|^D3_.|^D4_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x)))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
prungap$scoreplus <- (rowSums(prungap[grep("^D1_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / apply(prungap[grep("^D1_.",cocoavars3full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
prungap$evaluation <- ifelse(is.na(prungap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) > 0.3,"No Evidence of Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) > 0.2 & apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) <= 0.3,"Evidence of Minimum Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) > 0.1 & apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) <= 0.2,"Evidence of Good Adoption",
                                    ifelse(apply(prungap[c("scoreC","scoreD")], 1, max) <= 0.1,"Evidence of Excellent Adoption","NA"))))) #evaluation of all criteria together
prungap$evaluationplus <- ifelse(is.na(prungap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(prungap[c("scoreplus")], 1, max) >= 0.3,"Additionaly Evidence of Recent Pruning","No Additional Evidence of Recent Pruning")) #evaluation extra criteria
prungapfinal <- (prungap[c("S_FID","NAcheck","scoreC","scoreD","scoreplus","evaluation","evaluationplus")]) #filter only cases for cass only
colnames(prungapfinal)[1] <- "C1"
write.table(prungapfinal, "CocoaFarm_pruningManagement.txt", sep="\t")
print(head(prungapfinal))

Cocoa Farm Intercropping

Changelog: allow ^F4_.$ option 4(cannot identify) to be valid to indicate root-crop diveristy

cocoavars4 <- grep("^S_FID$|^F1_.|^F2_.SUM|^F3_.|^F4_.SUM|^F5_.|^F6_.|^F7_.", names(cocoavisit), value=TRUE) #select only inte management variables
integap <- cocoavisit[cocoavars4] #data table for inte GAP
cocoavars4full <- grep("^F1_.|^F2_.SUM|^F3_.|^F4_.SUM|^F5_.|^F6_.|^F7_.", names(integap), value=TRUE) #select only countable score variables
integap[grep("^F1_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F1_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F3_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F3_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F5_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F5_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F6_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F6_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F7_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F7_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F2_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F2_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1:11=1;else=NA") #recoding values
integap[grep("^F4_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(integap[grep("^F4_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)]),"1:4=1;else=NA") #recoding values
integap$F2_sum <- rowSums(cbind(rowSums(integap[grep("^F2_.SUM_1",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2,rowSums(integap[grep("^F2_.SUM_2",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2,rowSums(integap[grep("^F2_.SUM_3",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2),na.rm=TRUE) #count circles with min.2 fruit tree species
integap$F4_sum <- rowSums(cbind(rowSums(integap[grep("^F4_.SUM_1",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2,rowSums(integap[grep("^F4_.SUM_2",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2,rowSums(integap[grep("^F4_.SUM_3",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) >= 2),na.rm=TRUE) #count circles with min.2 root crop species
integap$NAcheck <- ifelse((apply(integap[grep("^F1_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(integap[grep("^F7_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))) & (apply(integap[grep("^F1_.|^F3_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x)))) == 
apply(integap[grep("^F5_.|^F6_.",cocoavars4,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(is.na(x))))),"1",NA) #checks that for every observation component the same number of trees have been checked
integap$score <- (rowSums(integap[grep("^F1_.|^F3_.|^F5_.|^F6_.|^F7_.",cocoavars4full,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) / ((apply(integap[grep("^F1_.|^F3_.|^F5_.|^F6_.|^F7_.",cocoavars4full,value=TRUE)],1,function(x) length(which(!is.na(x))))) / 5)  #scores per entry and category, ignoring NA
integap$scoreplus <- (rowSums(integap[c("F2_sum","F4_sum")],na.rm=TRUE)) / 3  #scores average number of circles which had at least 2 observations of each crop type
integap$evaluation <- ifelse(is.na(integap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(integap["score"], 1, max) == 0,"No Evidence of Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(integap["score"], 1, max) > 0 & apply(integap["score"], 1, max) <= 1,"Evidence of Minimum Adoption",
                             ifelse(apply(integap["score"], 1, max) > 1 & apply(integap["score"], 1, max) <= 3,"Evidence of Good Adoption",
                                    ifelse(apply(integap["score"], 1, max) > 3,"Evidence of Excellent Adoption","NA"))))) #evaluation of all criteria together
integap$evaluationplus <- ifelse(is.na(integap$NAcheck),NA,ifelse(apply(integap[c("scoreplus")], 1, max) >= 0.5,"Additionaly Evidence of High Intercropping Diversity","No Additional Evidence of High Intercropping Diversity")) #evaluation extra criteria

                                                         ifelse((hhvegegap$Q131 == 1 & hhvegegap$Q130 == 0),1,0)) #summarize score of Q131 into Q130
hhvegegapres <- hhvegegap[grep("^C1$|^S3_4$|^Q129$|^Q130$|^Q134$|^Q132$|^Q133$", names(hhvegegap), value=TRUE)] #new variable with only the summary score results and farmer ID

hhvegegapres$evaluationNArm <- recode(hhvegegapres$percNArm,"0:30='a) No Evidence of Adoption';31:50='b) Evidence of Minimum Adoption';51:70='c) Evidence of Good Adoption';71:100='d) Evidence of Excellent Adoption'")

Cocoa Farm Rehabilitation Rubric

When using Dummy-Data please observe that IDs between cocoa farm visit and hhvisit need to match for the code to work

rehabvars1 <- grep("^S_FID$|^H10$|^PM2$|^H2_.|^H2A_.|^B3_.|^B2_.|^H4_.|^H9_.|^H5_.|^H6_.|^H7_.|^H3_.|^H8_.", names(cocoavisit), value=TRUE) #select only rehab variables
rehab <- cocoavisit[rehabvars1] #data table for rehab
rehabvarsfull <- names(rehab[grep("^H10$|^PM2$|^H2_.|^H2A_.|^B3_.|^B2_.|^H4_.|^H9_.|^H5_.|^H6_.|^H7_.|^H3_.|^H8_.",names(rehab),value=TRUE)]) #variables of farm visit without IDs
rehab[grep("^H5_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(rehab[grep("^H5_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=0;2=1;else=NA") #recoding values
rehab[grep("^H6_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(rehab[grep("^H6_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
rehab[grep("^H7_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)] <- recode(unlist(rehab[grep("^H7_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]),"1=1;2=0;else=NA") #recoding values
d <- unname(unlist(rehab[grep("^H8_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)])) #prepare vector of all values of H8
rehab[grep("^H2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)] <- ifelse(rehab[grep("^H2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]==1, 
                                                           recode(unlist(rehab[grep("^H2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]),"else=100"),
                                                           recode(unlist(rehab[grep("^H2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)]),"else=d")) #conditional recoding depending on H8
rehab$farmsize <- rehab$PM2
rehab$youngplantdensity <- ((rowSums(rehab[grep("^B3_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)], na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * pi * 10^2 /10000)) #estimated young plant density (part a) as part of observation circle underplanting
rehab$youngplanttotal <- ((rowSums(rehab[grep("^B3_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)], na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * pi * 10^2 /10000)) * rehab$PM2  #estimated young plant total count (part a) as part of observation circle underplanting
rehab$matureplanttotal <- ((rowSums(rehab[grep("^B2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)], na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * pi * 10^2 /10000)) * rehab$PM2  #estimated mature plant total count as part of observation circle underplanting
rehab$matureplantdensity <- ((rowSums(rehab[grep("^B2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)], na.rm=TRUE)) / (3 * pi * 10^2 /10000))  #estimated mature plant density as part of observation circle underplanting
rehab$newplotsize <- (rowSums(rehab[grep("^H8_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) + (rowSums(rehab[grep("^H3_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) *10000)) #estimation of area of distinguishable replanting plots
rehab$youngplantestimation <- (((rowSums(rehab[grep("^H4_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) + (rowSums(rehab[grep("^H9_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE))) / rowSums(rehab[grep("^H2_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE)) * (rowSums(rehab[grep("^H8_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) + (rowSums(rehab[grep("^H3_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) *10000)) #estimate total number of young plants on farm as part of new farm plots
rehab$newploteval <- rowSums(rehab[grep("^H5_.|^H6_.|^H7_.",rehabvars1,value=TRUE)],na.rm=TRUE) #score likeliness of farmer having created a new plot from other land-use
rehab$areascore <- ifelse(is.na(rehab$farmsize) | rehab$farmsize==0,NA,(rehab$newplotsize / (10000 * rehab$farmsize)) * 100) #percentage rehabilitation by area through replanting
rehab$plantscore <- ifelse(is.na(rehab$matureplanttotal) | rehab$matureplanttotal==0,NA,(rehab$youngplanttotal / (rehab$matureplanttotal)) * 100) #percentage rehabilitation by plant count through underplanting
rehab$score <- rehab$areascore + rehab$plantscore #combining both percentatges
rehab$evaluation <- ifelse((rehab$youngplanttotal==0 | is.na(rehab$youngplanttotal)) & (rehab$youngplantestimation == 0 | is.na(rehab$youngplantestimation)),"No Evidence of Adoption","Evidence of Adoption")
rehab$evaluationscore <- ifelse(rehab$score >=3,"Evidence of at least 3% Rehabilitation","No Evidence of at least 3% Rehabilitation")
rehab$evaluationplus <- ifelse(rehab$newploteval==3,"Strong Evidence of Farm Extension",
                               ifelse(rehab$newploteval==2,"Slight Evidence of Farm Extension","No Evidence of Farm Extension"))
numbfarms <- hhsurvey[c("C1","S1")] #extract the number of farms per farmer from hh survey
colnames(numbfarms) <- c("S_FID","NumberOfFarms") #re-name columns for merge
rehab2 <- merge(rehab,numbfarms,by="S_FID") #merge data tables based on ID
rehabfinal<- rehab2[c("S_FID","farmsize","newplotsize","newploteval","youngplantdensity","youngplanttotal","matureplantdensity","matureplanttotal","youngplantestimation","score","evaluation","evaluationplus","evaluationscore","NumberOfFarms")]
colnames(rehabfinal)[1] <- "C1"
write.table(rehabfinal, "FarmRehabilitation.txt", sep="\t")
print(head(rehabfinal))
